diff --git a/src/go/hello_world_test.go b/src/go/hello_world_test.go
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..5ebdc3f
--- /dev/null
+++ b/src/go/hello_world_test.go
@@ -0,0 +1,31 @@
+package main
+
+import (
+    "testing"
+    "bytes"
+    "os"
+    "io"
+)
+
+func captureOutput(f func()) string {
+    r, w, _ := os.Pipe()
+    stdout := os.Stdout
+    os.Stdout = w
+
+    f()
+
+    w.Close()
+    os.Stdout = stdout
+
+    var buf bytes.Buffer
+    io.Copy(&buf, r)
+    return buf.String()
+}
+
+func TestHelloWorld(t *testing.T) {
+    output := captureOutput(main)
+    expected := "Hello World\n"
+    if output != expected {
+        t.Errorf("expected %q but got %q", expected, output)
+    }
+}
